        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Patient Access Protection Act</b></p> <p>This bill eliminates certain reductions to Medicaid disproportionate share hospital (DSH) allotments. (DSHs are hospitals that receive additional payment under Medicaid for treating a large share of low-income patients.)</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
